				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Marloon and Pyrov...what's the matter with you?  Who cares what the actual legal merits are?  The fact is, this is a game, and if you buy plat for RL$, you are cheating.  Period.  And yantis, etc. is violating Sony's EULA and helping people cheat.  It's no different from stealing money out of the bank if you're playing Monopoly.  Or giving your little brother a dollar for a Monopoly 500.  Cheating.
<br />

<br />
I don't know whether or not there is a good solution to the problem; the debate on that subject seems endless.  However, if you're buying plat, you are a cheater and you are an A-Hole.<br />_________________<br />Glaven Hoivenmaven
